test_large_range:
assert [23, 24] == [24]
  
  At index 0 diff: 23 != 24
  Left contains one more item: 24
  
  Full diff:
    [
  +     23,
        24,
    ]
test_even_range:
assert [46, 48] == [48]
  
  At index 0 diff: 46 != 48
  Left contains one more item: 48
  
  Full diff:
    [
  +     46,
        48,
    ]
